<rml>
<head>
	<title>Person Quest</title>
	<link type="text/rcss" href="PersonQuestWidget.rcss"/>
</head>
<body>
	<div id="quest-root">
		<div id="quest-panel">
			<div class="quest-badge">QUEST 03</div>
			<div class="quest-title">사람 치기</div>
			<div class="quest-body">지나가는 사람을 힘껏 치세요.</div>
			<button id="person-quest-ok-button" class="quest-button">Okay</button>
		</div>
	</div>
</body>
</rml>
